headline: Want $5,100 in Annual Dividends? Invest $29,000 in Each of These 3 Stocks.
summary: Stocks that pay a dividend aren't doing well these days as high interest rates make for enticing alternatives, but that can present an attractive opportunity to load up on them, as many are offering attractive payouts.  Three stocks that can help generate a ton of revenue for your portfolio today are Verizon Communications (NYSE: VZ), Enbridge (NYSE: ENB), and T. Rowe Price Group (NASDAQ: TROW).  Verizon's stock has struggled over the past five years, falling more than 12%.
